snippet.title: The Family Man S3 - Official Trailer | Raj & DK | Manoj Bajpayee, Jaideep Ahlawat | Prime Video IN
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
The Family Man Season 3 Official Trailer 

SERIES:
"The Family Man," created by Raj & DK, an edgy and thrilling series on Prime Video, follows the life of Srikant Tiwari, a seemingly ordinary middle-class man who secretly works for the Threat Assessment and Surveillance Cell( TASC), a fictional cell of the National Investigation Agency in Mumbai. Balancing the demands of his high-stakes job and his family, life proves increasingly challenging as Srikant navigates dangerous missions against terrorists while trying to be a present husband and father. As he dives deeper into the murky world of espionage, Srikant must protect his loved ones from the perils of his covert profession, all while grappling with moral dilemmas that test his integrity and loyalty.

SEASON:
Outlawed and on the run, Srikant Tiwari faces sinister forces threatening to ignite chaos in Northeast India, uncovering a conspiracy that could plunge the nation into war.

Created by: Raj & DK

Directed by: Raj & DK, Suman Kumar, Tusshar Seyth
Produced by: Raj & DK

localized.description:
Prime Video India Presents
The Family Man Season 3 Official Trailer 

SERIES:
"The Family Man," created by Raj & DK, an edgy and thrilling series on Prime Video, follows the life of Srikant Tiwari, a seemingly ordinary middle-class man who secretly works for the Threat Assessment and Surveillance Cell( TASC), a fictional cell of the National Investigation Agency in Mumbai. Balancing the demands of his high-stakes job and his family, life proves increasingly challenging as Srikant navigates dangerous missions against terrorists while trying to be a present husband and father. As he dives deeper into the murky world of espionage, Srikant must protect his loved ones from the perils of his covert profession, all while grappling with moral dilemmas that test his integrity and loyalty.

SEASON:
Outlawed and on the run, Srikant Tiwari faces sinister forces threatening to ignite chaos in Northeast India, uncovering a conspiracy that could plunge the nation into war.

#MichaelMovie

MICHAEL is the cinematic portrayal of the life and legacy of one of the most influential artists the world has ever known. The film tells the story of Michael Jackson‚Äôs life beyond the music, tracing his journey from the discovery of his extraordinary talent as the lead of the Jackson Five, to the visionary artist whose creative ambition fueled a relentless pursuit to become the biggest entertainer in the world. Highlighting both his life off-stage and some of the most iconic performances from his early solo career, the film gives audiences a front-row seat to Michael Jackson as never before. This is where his story begins.

#NewSong2025 #NewHindiSong #RomanticSong #EmraanHashmi #YamiGautam #EmraanYami #HindiSong #HindiNewSong #NewRomanticSong #NewHindiSong2025 #EmraanHashmiNewSong #YamiGautamNewSong #RomanticSongHindi #HindiSong2025 #BetaabDil #SaritDutta

‚ÄúBetaab Dil‚Äù is a heart-touching romantic Hindi song that brings back the golden era of 90s Bollywood music. Sung and composed by Sarit Dutta, this soulful melody beautifully captures the emotions of love, longing, and separation. The heartfelt lyrics by Dr. Uma Naveen Mehta paint a timeless picture of a betaab (restless) heart waiting for its beloved.

If you miss the charm of classic love songs, ‚ÄúBetaab Dil‚Äù will take you straight back to that nostalgic era of melody and emotion.

üéß Experience ‚ÄúBetaab Dil‚Äù ‚Äî A Pure Hindi Romantic Love Song
Close your eyes, feel the rhythm, and let this song remind you of the beautiful simplicity of true love. Perfect for anyone who believes in eternal romance and misses the soulful tunes of the 90s

üëâ Don‚Äôt forget to LIKE, SHARE & SUBSCRIBE for more soulful music.

Subscribe : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCWj7oD9SuDcGciiBQT9BQuw?sub_confirmation=1
__________________________________________________

Song Credits
Song : Betaab Dil
Singer : Sarit Dutta
Music Composer : Sarit Dutta
Lyrics : Dr Uma Naveen Mehta
Backing Vocals : Subhajit Das
Music Produced, Mixed & Mastered by Sarit Dutta @ Rivertone Studio
__________________________________________________

Lyrics:-

Hum chahe itna hi 
Ab tera saath ho
Kya tune kabhi ye jana
Kitna dard hai mujhko

Bekhudi mein chal pade hai
Khudko hi ab mitane
Mere kadam rukte nahi 
Teri galiyon me aane se

Deewangi ki had se jyada
Hum karte hai ye pyaar tumko
Ankhon mein teri yaadein wo leke
Betaab dil chahe tujhko

Baaton ne teri
Mujhko saari raat jagaya
Sanson ne teri
Mujhko yu apna banaya

Koi lamha nahi hai mera
Jisme tu nazar na aaya
Na hamne koi khata ki
fir kyu tune di hai saja

Deewangi ki had se jyada
Hum karte hai ye pyaar tumko
Ankhon mein teri yaadein wo leke
Betaab dil chahe tujhko

Title : Ankhai Baimani ( Official Music Video )

‚ÄúAnkhai Baimani‚Äù is where Nepali folk soul meets modern urban rhythm. This song blends the raw essence of traditional melody with fresh new-age sound design ‚Äî a perfect fusion of old and new generations of Nepali music.

The music video captures the spirit of cultural evolution: traditional attire, instruments, and settings merging beautifully with contemporary style, symbolizing how love, art, and identity transcend time.

‚ú® Experience the emotion, nostalgia, and energy of a timeless Nepali vibe reimagined for today‚Äôs listeners.

Audio credits :
Lyrics/ Music/ Vox : Almoda Rana Uprety
Mix / Master : Almoda Rana Uprety
Sarangi : Hemant Kanchha Rasaily
Guitar : Bishal Chhetri 

Video Credits:
Choreography : The Wings 
Band members : 
Bass : Sujit Shahi 
Drums : Ashish Shrestha
Sarangi : Anil Gandharba 
Camera : Sanzip Rai, Jensih Newa, Chakra Pulami Magar 
AD : Santosh Rana Magar
Production Manager : Bishal Karkee
Edit : Sanzip Rai, Chakra Pulami Magar

Tune in to all your favorite Bhakti songs and mantras on the Saregama Bhakti App.
Download now: https://sarega.ma/bhakti_yt

Saregama is India's oldest music label and has a never ending library of the most popular devotional songs, bhajans, aartis and puja vidhis. Saregama Bhakti is focussed on bringing you quality devotional and spiritual content sung by the legends of Bollywood, Devotional and Spiritual genre like Lata Mangeshkar, Jagjit Singh, Anup Jalota, Hari Om Sharan, Suresh Wadkar and many more. Right from Bhajans, Pooja Vidhis, Gurbani, Sai Bhakti we have it all available on your channel to help to enhance your divine experience and connect with the almighty at a new level.

snippet.title: Dayglow - Can I Call You Tonight?
snippet.description:
Dayglow - Can I Call You Tonight?

(Lyrics):
[Verse 1]
I feel close
Well, maybe I'm not, heaven knows
It's a spotlight stuck on the ceiling
Why are these the things that I'm feeling?
There's so much time
For me to speak up, but I keep quiet
I'll complicate the most of the mantra
The power's out and I can't turn the fan on

[Chorus]
So can I call you tonight?
I'm trying to make up my mind
Just how I feel
Could you tell me what's real?
I hear your voice on the phone
Now I'm no longer alone
Just how I feel
Could you tell me what's real anymore?
'Cause I wouldn't know

[Verse 2]
Voice so low
Sneaking around, so it goes
I always try my best to listen
Picking up things that I can fidget
Circle speed
Pacing around, watching my feet
Batteries drain, I get the memo
"I think that I might have to let you go"

[Chorus]
So can I call you tonight?
I'm trying to make up my mind
Just how I feel
Could you tell me what's real?
I hear your voice on the phone
Now I'm no longer alone
Just how I feel
Could you tell me what's real anymore?
'Cause I wouldn't know

[Bridge]
(We're sorry; you have reached a number that has been disconnected or is no longer in service)
(If you feel you have reached this recording in error, please check the number and try your call again)
Don't go, don't go so easy
Don't go, don't go and leave me
Don't go, don't go so easy
Don't go, don't go and leave me
Don't go, don't go so easy
Don't go, don't go and leave me
Don't go, don't go so easy
Don't go, go

[Chorus]
So can I call you tonight?
I'm trying to make up my mind
Just how I feel
Could you tell me what's real?
I hear your voice on the phone
Now I'm no longer alone
Just how I feel
Could you tell me what's real anymore?
'Cause I wouldn't know

[Outro]
(Yeah, I wouldn't know)
(I wouldn't know)
(Yeah, I wouldn't know)
(Just how I feel)
(I wouldn't know)
